				<font face="verdana" size="1"><b><u>Detailed Statistics</b></u></font></a><br><br>


						
					 	<br><br>		
						<table align="left" background="http://www.everlore.com/gimages/trick.jpg" width="100%" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="1" bordercolor="#979797" bordercolordark="#979797" bordercolorlight="#979797">
